  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan over medium\u2011high heat.",
    "In a bowl, toss the shrimp with olive oil, smoked paprika, crushed red pepper, salt, and black pepper until coated.",
    "Grill the shrimp for 2\u20133 minutes per side, or until pink and cooked through; transfer to a plate and let rest.",
    "Meanwhile, whisk together the heavy cream and lime juice until smooth; season with a pinch of salt.",
    "In a large salad bowl, combine the grilled shrimp, diced avocado, sliced red onion, diced tomato, and chopped cilantro.",
    "Pour the lime\u2011cream sauce over the salad and gently toss to coat all ingredients.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with more salt, pepper, or lime juice if desired.",
    "Serve immediately over mixed greens or with toasted corn tortillas for a complete meal."
